  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "ORACLE's stochastic prophecy feeds as FM audio into ORGANON's metabolic organism — over 60 seconds, each new oracle distribution morph changes what the organism eats, producing a layered evolution of metabolic character that never settles.",
